{"tid":2377191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不滿當地立法強迫付新聞費  Google威脅禁澳搜尋","createTime":"2021-01-23T11:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T20:00:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cfd991693e638a9828751f279302c173bdff9108","tid":2377191,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:32:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210123/7KULTN4TJJFWTIGLG4NQ7FUXWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210123%2F7KULTN4TJJFWTIGLG4NQ7FUXWE%2F&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TavilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=986861a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210123%2F7KULTN4TJJFWTIGLG4NQ7FUXWE%2F&h=f1344952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210123/7KULTN4TJJFWTIGLG4NQ7FUXWE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n不滿當地立法強迫付新聞費 <br />\nGoogle威脅禁澳搜尋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ve8W2niyrlBJyFefjZ9DH_cYaG0=/1367x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BVF2SUMIDJGK7L324JRSPL6K74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVe8W2niyrlBJyFefjZ9DH_cYaG0%3D%2F1367x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBVF2SUMIDJGK7L324JRSPL6K74.jpg&h=35b27d5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■澳洲的新法案旨在迫使Google和fb等平台向當地新聞機構付款。 互聯網<br />\n<br />\n澳洲政府擬今年內立法，規定網上平台分享當地新聞內容時，須向相關媒體付費；反對立法的Google繼封殺主流新聞網後，昨日揚言中止當地搜尋服務；反觀Google在法國則「跪低」，前日與一批紙媒達成付費協議，是歐洲首例。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：是否續封特朗普 fb交「法院」決定<br />\n<br />\n去年澳洲推動立法，強制Google與facebook在平台分享新聞內容時，須向相關媒體付費，分享收益，否則面臨罰款。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n莫里森：我們不受威嚇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CNOX1kFkj1dwriX9xZZx_UFM-DY=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XSZFU3R5GRDLNHL2BLSJKUQ2D4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCNOX1kFkj1dwriX9xZZx_UFM-DY%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXSZFU3R5GRDLNHL2BLSJKUQ2D4.jpg&h=396d1781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Google澳紐區董事總經理席爾瓦（右）昨以視像參與澳洲國會聽證會。 美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/irC2UeYdx7awshbBlJPmdY1Gv0U=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GRLCGYZWOVFYFNGHEMFGPXZMME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FirC2UeYdx7awshbBlJPmdY1Gv0U%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGRLCGYZWOVFYFNGHEMFGPXZMME.jpg&h=11fd786c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■莫理森指不會被Google的警告嚇倒。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGoogle澳洲及新西蘭地區董事總經理席爾瓦（Melanie Silva），。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n席爾瓦說，搜尋大前提是網絡之間須百分百相連，立法將限制 Google日後能搜尋的網站，並引發「無法控制的財務和運作風險」；若法案通過，最壞結果是公司「別無選擇」要中止當地網絡搜尋服務。目前Google在澳洲網絡搜尋市場佔有率約95%。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲總理莫里森聞訊強調，澳洲的法規都是由政府經國會訂立，亦是當地一貫做事方式，「能夠接受的人我們無任歡迎，但我們不會理會威嚇」。<br />\n<br />\n澳媒上周已報道Google疑似搞小動作，悄悄封鎖多間主流新聞網，包括當地新聞網瀏覽第一的澳洲廣播公司、梅鐸旗下新聞集團報章以及澳洲版《衞報》；用戶搜尋時以舊連結取代，或是呈現其他網站內容。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。，澳洲人在武漢肺炎和山火肆虐期間都極倚賴新聞資訊，若Google真的如此任意封鎖新聞網，在聽證會聲稱「新聞有價」的高層便是自打嘴巴，「新聞在他們眼中僅如寵物影片吧」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾與法國協商終跪低付款<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，Google前日在法國與代表多間傳媒的團體APIG達成版權付費協議，協議框架列明每日出版量、每月的網絡流量、政治和一般資訊比例等，是歐洲首例。這個先例將有助其他印刷媒體與Google達成個別協議，從網上賺回流失的利潤。<br />\n<br />\n一如澳洲情況，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲廣播公司/路透社/中央社"},{"pid":"892cf0abc65cf7385256d877e6a68ccdc5fca930","tid":2377191,"uid":164055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T19:29:39.000Z","msg":"big tech<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a82fd8108b54cfe78c0a4b81137f669e2b2742","tid":2377191,"uid":214679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T19:32:31.000Z","msg":"搬石頭砸自己的腳"},{"pid":"6ab3797dc661ebcc4c84981fcae45aaa9ec4a237","tid":2377191,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T19:41:24.000Z","msg":"Google喺搜尋結果顯示新聞網站都算使用咗佢內容？唔係好明點解要俾錢"},{"pid":"f0a897515ffb9fc38257d81198c6adba5d9a8bd2","tid":2377191,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"56a82fd8108b54cfe78c0a4b81137f669e2b2742","tid":2377191,"uid":214679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T19:32:31.000Z","msg":"搬石頭砸自己的腳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T19:58:13.000Z","msg":"跟手入支那咪又係跟足規距，google正一仆街公司"},{"pid":"f29f19b248f60fc8e8f4207ea7cfa767bbd839af","tid":2377191,"uid":256837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T20:00:50.000Z","msg":"google係時候收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}